## Version 8.4.5

- added default templates for application and project home pages
- added default rewrite rules to route requests to the new home page templates
- added new action `webPage` to serve the new templates
- deprecated the `rewrite` config option in favor of `rewriteRules`
- `assets` defaults to `/data/assets` if that directory exists, otherwise to null
- deprecated the `index` and `project` assets in favor of the `application.home` and `project.home` templates
- deprecated the `errorPage` option in favor of the `application.error` template

## Version 8.4.4

- added Postgres storage provider

## Version 8.4.3

- CSV exporter
- optimized GDAL-related vector processing

## Version 8.4.2

- shapefile, KML and GML exporters
- update SSL configuration to the Mozilla intermediate profile

## Version 8.4.1

- basic feature export framework
- configuration now accepts multiple comma-separated paths
- improved config error reporting 

## Version 8.4.0

- added functions to scale GDAL rasters
- fixed CRS transformation issues for certain projections
- fixed concurrency issues with temporary files
